original_text: and out of the tribe of Naphtali: Kedesh in Galilee with its pasturelands, Hammon with its pasturelands, and Kiriathaim with its pasturelands.
korean_text: 납달리 지파 중에서 갈릴리의 게데스와 그 초원과 함몬과 그 초원과 기랴다임과 그 초원을 주니라

sentences.original_text: and out of the tribe of Naphtali
Kedesh in Galilee with its pasturelands
